How to test kafka event

1. Turn on Kafka server 

bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat config\kraft\server.properties

new kafka 
2. Create topic
>bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic activity.events.v1 --from-beginning --property print.key=true --property print.value=true --property key.separator=:

3. Poll topic 

cd C:\kafka>bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic activity.events.v1 --property print.key=true

4. Create activity

http://localhost:8082/api/v1/activity/new
{
  "userId":1,
  "type":"RUNNING",
  "duration":45,
  "caloriesBurned":400,
  "startTime":"2026-02-17T06:30:00",
  "additionalMetrics":
  {
    "distanceKm":5.2,
    "avgHeartRate":140
  }
}

